org.sat4j.specs

インタフェース SearchListener<S extends ISolverService>

  • すべてのスーパーインタフェース:
    java.io.Serializable
    既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    ConflictDepthTracing, ConflictLevelTracing, ConflictTracing, DecisionLevelTracing, DecisionTracing, DotSearchTracing, HeuristicsTracing, LBDTracing, LearnedClauseSizeTracing, LearnedClausesSizeTracing, LearnedTracing, ManyCore, ManyCoreIntegerPB, ManyCorePB, MultiTracing, PreprocCardConstrLearningSolver, RupSearchListener, SearchEnumeratorListener, SearchListenerAdapter, SearchMinOneListener, SearchOptimizerListener, SpeedTracing, TextOutputTracing

    public interface SearchListener<S extends ISolverService>
extends java.io.Serializable
    Interface to the solver main steps. Useful for integrating search visualization or debugging. (that class moved from org.sat4j.minisat.core in earlier version of SAT4J).
    導入されたバージョン:
    2.1
